title: 132: Cubs of the NFL and game picks
itunes:title: 132: Cubs of the NFL and game picks
description:
Former NFL scouts Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks discuss how the success of building the Chicago Cubs and winning a title parallels with NFL teams. The duo also makes their projections for Week 9 of NFL action and college football.
